sudosrv (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of sudosrv
  * Implements sudo_logsrv.proto protocol
  * Supports dual-mode operation (local storage and relay)
  * Includes TLS support for secure log transmission
  * Store-and-forward caching for upstream server reliability
  * Full sudoers compatibility for log path customization
  * Systemd service integration

 -- Paul Kilar <pkilar@gmail.com>  Mon, 17 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000
